casebody.data:
RECONSIDERATION OF PRIOR DECISIONS

2009-2058. State ex rel. Daimler Chrysler Corp. v. Indus. Comm.

Franklin App. No. 08AP-1017, 2009-Ohio-5778. Reported at 127 Ohio St.3d 1433, 2010-Ohio-5500, 936 N.E.2d 962. On motion for reconsideration. Motion granted. Appellant shall file a brief within 20 days of the date of this entry, and the parties shall otherwise proceed in accordance with S.Ct.Prac.R. 6.2 - 6.7. As provided in S.Ct.Prac. R. 6.7, the court may dismiss this case or take other action if the parties fail to timely file merit briefs.
